<section class="case-study__section--white case-study--background">
	<div class="wrapper">
		<h2>Background</h2>
		<div class="row cf">
			<div class="col3"></div>
			<div class="col7">
				<p>Beach Front Villas are a new start up business who provide luxury villa rentals on the stunning Turks &amp; Caicos Islands in the Caribbean. Robin Spruce, Beach Front Villas owner and founder, approached us to produce a class leading, visually stunning and easy to use website. The site we designed and built puts the fantastic islands and amazing luxury villas to the fore and firmly estamblshes Beach Front Villas as leaders within their market.</p>
			</div>
